'From Squeak2.9alpha of 13 June 2000 [latest update: #2911] on 29 October 2000 at 9:15:07 pm'!"Change Set:		ThreeFixes-arDate:			29 October 2000Author:			Andreas RaabThree fixes for Alan."!!Morph methodsFor: 'meta-actions' stamp: 'ar 10/29/2000 21:04'!buildHandleMenu: aHand	"Build the morph menu for the given morph's halo's menu handle. This menu has two sections. The first section contains commands that are interpreted by the hand; the second contains commands provided by the target morph. This method allows the morph to decide which items should be included in the hand's section of the menu."	| menu |	menu _ MenuMorph new defaultTarget: self.	menu addStayUpItem.	self addAddHandMenuItemsForHalo: menu hand: aHand.	menu defaultTarget: self.	self addCustomHaloMenuItems: menu hand: aHand.	menu addLine.	self player ifNotNil: [self player addPlayerMenuItemsTo: menu hand: aHand].	menu defaultTarget: aHand.	^ menu! !!SketchEditorMorph methodsFor: 'morphic' stamp: 'ar 10/29/2000 21:13'!mouseDown: evt	"Start a new stroke.  Check if any palette setting have changed.  6/11/97 20:30 tk"	| cur pfPen myAction |	"verify that we are in a good state"	self verifyState: evt.		"includes prepareToPaint and #scalingOrRotate"	pfPen _ self get: #paintingFormPen for: evt.	undoBuffer _ paintingForm deepCopy.	"know we will draw something"	pfPen place: (evt cursorPoint - bounds origin).	myAction _ self getActionFor: evt.	myAction == #paint: ifTrue:[		palette recentColor: (self getColorFor: evt)].	self set: #strokeOrigin for: evt to: evt cursorPoint.		"origin point for pickup: rect: ellispe: polygon: line: star:.  Always take it."	myAction == #pickup: ifTrue: [		cur _ Cursor corner clone.		cur offset: 0@0  "cur offset abs".		evt hand showTemporaryCursor: cur].	myAction == #polygon: ifTrue: [self polyNew: evt].	"a mode lets you drag vertices"	self mouseMove: evt.! !TextPlusPasteUpMorph removeSelector: #handlesMouseDown:!TextPlusPasteUpMorph removeSelector: #mouseDown:!